data.description: Welcome to 223 Footprint Rd, nestled in the quiet community of Pocono Highland Lake Estates. This charming Cape Cod with lots of potential would make a great starter home. Inside, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, a cozy dining room with a brick-faced fireplace, and a generous-sized living room perfect for gatherings. The unfinished room off the primary bedroom offers endless possibilities—it could become a laundry room and office, a huge walk-in closet, or a tranquil reading room. This home also boasts a one-car garage and a full basement for storage or additional living space. With two laundry hook-up areas and a gas furnace for efficient heating, household chores are a breeze. Schedule a showing today to experience the comfort, convenience, and charm of this lovely property!
